## Mirrors
$$
m = \frac{f}{f-u} 
$$
and
$$
m = \frac{f-v}{f} 
$$
## Lens
$$
m = \frac{f}{f+u} 
$$
and
$$
m = \frac{f-v}{f} 
$$

